  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the safety and efficacy of G-CSF-mobilized
      autologous peripheral blood mononuclear cell injection to ischemic limbs of patients with
      critical limb ischemia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
